historical relations between Mozambique and its traditional
partners.
</P>
<P>
Chissano expressed his wish that the cooperation between his
country and France be strengthened, saying that French investment
in eight projects in the southern African country from 1985 to
1997 was only 72 million U.S. Dollars.
</P>
<P>
