peace-loving nation, and would provide aid to help all Arabs and
Muslims solve their problems.
</P>
<P>
The king's remarks was another indication that the prolonged
deadlock in the Israeli-Palestinian peace process has caused
increasing concern among the Arab world.
</P>
<P>
Saudi Arabia has already voiced its support to the call by
Palestinian leader Yasser Arafat to convene an Arab summit to
confront Israel's policy of intransigence. 
