<HEADLINE> Chinese, Belarussian Foreign Ministers Hold Talks in Beijing </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 30 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Foreign Minister Tang
Jiaxuan said here today that China is ready to work for the
development of long-term and stable Sino-Belarussian relations.
