<P>
Antonovich said Belarus considers it a foreign policy priority
to develop friendly ties with China. The two nations hold similar
positions on major global issues, he added.
</P>
<P>
Belarus supports China's position on the issues of Taiwan and
Tibet, Antonovich said, and Belarus is ready to increase bilateral
cooperation of mutual benefit at various levels.
</P>
<P>
The two ministers also exchanged views on international
issues of common concern. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
