<HEADLINE> Liberty Beats Mercury in WNBA Game </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, June 29 (Xinhua) -- Vickie Johnson and Sophia
Witherspoon each scored 23 points to help the New York Liberty
remain unbeaten at home with a 71-68 win over the Phoenix Mercuy
in a WNBA game on Monday night.
</P>
<P>
It was the Liberty's fourth straight victory. The Mercury's
three-game winning streak was snapped.
</P>
<P>
