rebounds, and Sandy Brondello added 19 points for the Shock.
</P>
<P>
Detroit snapped Charlotte's five-game winning streak to gain
their fifth straight victory.
</P>
<P>
Andrea Congreaes led Charlotte with 10 points.
</P>
<P>
Cynthia Cooper hit 16 points and Kim Perrot added 11 for the
Comets, who overcame a 3-of-14 effort from three-point range by
making 20-of-27 free throws.
</P>
<P>
Alessandra Santos de Oliveira scored 16 points for the Mystics,
whose 48 points matched the league season-low. 
