</P>
<P>
-- Some confusion continues to persist about the government's
official line vis-a-vis the issue of conversion of the Line of
Control into the international border with Pakistan.
</P>
<P>
The Economic Times:
</P>
<P>
-- Finance Minister Yashwant Sinha said Monday that the country
is coming out of recession and poised to achieve the targeted
growth rate. 
