were killed and 30 others injured when an overloaded bus skidded
off the road and tumbled into a roadside ditch. Four passengers
were killed on the spot while three others died on the way to
hospital.
</P>
<P>
The helper of the bus driver was driving the vehicle when the
accident took place, eye witnesses were quoted as saying. 
