<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-30 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Perez Joins Blackburn Club </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, June 29 (Xinhua) -- Sebastien Perez left French soccer
club Bastia on Monday to join England's Blackburn Rovers in a 4.9
million U.S. dollars transfer deal.
</P>
<P>
The 24-year-old defender has signed with Blackburn.
</P>
<P>
The five-year deal took Blackburn's off-season spending beyond
16.4 million U.S. dollars.
</P>
<P>
Perez said he agreed to terms with Blackburn because he had
given manager Roy Hodgson his word that if he left France it would
be to play for Blackburn Rovers. 
</P>
